The paper discusses multiple instance learning (MIL), which is a subfield of machine learning. MIL is often used in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) applications, as well as in information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) more broadly.
